{"surahDetails":{"id":94,"arabicName":"الشرح","banglaName":"বক্ষ প্রশস্তকরণ","englishName":"The Consolation","enTranslatedName":"Ash-Sharh","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","totalWords":27,"totalLetters":102,"audio":"http://download.quranicaudio.com/quran/ahmed_ibn_3ali_al-3ajamy/094.mp3","totalAyah":8},"surah":{"id":94,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"أَلَمۡ نَشۡرَحۡ لَكَ صَدۡرَكَ","bangl_text":"আমি কি আপনার বক্ষ উম্মুক্ত করে দেইনি","english_text":"Did We not expand for you, [O Muhammad], your breast","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/094001.mp3"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"وَوَضَعۡنَا عَنكَ وِزۡرَكَ","bangl_text":"আমি লাঘব করেছি আপনার বোঝা","english_text":"And We removed from you your burden","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/094002.mp3"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"ٱلَّذِيٓ أَنقَضَ ظَهۡرَكَ","bangl_text":"যা ছিল আপনার জন্যে অতিশয় দুঃসহ।","english_text":"Which had weighed upon your back","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/094003.mp3"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"وَرَفَعۡنَا لَكَ ذِكۡرَكَ","bangl_text":"আমি আপনার আলোচনাকে সমুচ্চ করেছি।","english_text":"And raised high for you your repute","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/094004.mp3"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"فَإِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرًا","bangl_text":"নিশ্চয় কষ্টের সাথে স্বস্তি রয়েছে।","english_text":"For indeed, with hardship [will be] ease","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/094005.mp3"},{"id":6,"arabic_text":"إِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرٗا","bangl_text":"নিশ্চয় কষ্টের সাথে স্বস্তি রয়েছে।","english_text":"Indeed, with hardship [will be] ease","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/094006.mp3"},{"id":7,"arabic_text":"فَإِذَا فَرَغۡتَ فَٱنصَبۡ","bangl_text":"অতএব, যখন অবসর পান পরিশ্রম করুন।","english_text":"So when you have finished [your duties], then stand up [for worship]","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/094007.mp3"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"وَإِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَٱرۡغَب","bangl_text":"এবং আপনার পালনকর্তার প্রতি মনোনিবেশ করুন।","english_text":"And to your Lord direct [your] longing","page":596,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/094008.mp3"}]}}